@@WGolden Mews@@N~
The mews on this tier has become a narrow residential lane where craft workers live above their ground-floor workshops. A potter's wheel is visible through an open door, and the steady hum of the wheel provides a rhythmic undertone to the ambient street sounds. The golden signboards are long gone, but a faded gilding trace on one lintel shows where the last one hung before it was taken down and repurposed.

