@@WIvory Passage@@N~
The passage on this tier has narrowed to barely more than an alley, the buildings on either side having been extended toward each other over the years until the gap between them admits only single-file foot traffic. The walls are close enough to touch with outstretched arms, and the effect is oddly intimate, like walking through a private corridor rather than a public street. A single wall sconce provides the only light, its flame guttering in the draft created by the passage's chimney-like proportions.

