@@WMoonlit Approach@@N~
The approach descends a half-step on this tier, creating a slightly sunken street that collects shadow even during the brightest hours. The @@yBank of Midgaard@@N occupies a fortified building on the south side, its entrance accessible via a short stairway from the street above, and a pair of iron-bracketed lanterns flanking the bank door provide the block's strongest light source. The buildings here are among the oldest in the lower city, their timber frames blackened with age and their stone foundations visibly subsiding in places.

