@@WLantern Promenade@@N~
The promenade's fifth tier is the last with a consistent run of @@ylantern@@N poles, their iron fixtures weathered to a rusty brown that blends with the common stone of the surrounding buildings. The walkway retains its wider-than-average dimensions but has lost the formal mustering-ground character of the upper tiers, serving instead as an informal gathering space for the lower-ward residents. A wooden stall selling roasted chestnuts and hot cider operates at the corner during the cooler months, its charcoal brazier adding warmth and a savoury smell to the evening air.

