This warden's authority derives from the Violet Compact â the civic agreement that bureaucratized rather than eradicated the flow of arcane materials through @@WMidgaard@@N. The violet band across their grey coat marks them as a licensed threshold inspector, empowered to demand documentation from anyone crossing with arcane goods. Their ledger is bound in pale leather and bears ward sigils that glow faintly when near unregistered materials.

~
