~
The road warden system was formalized during the Ash-and-Iron Decades, when raids severed @@WMidgaard@@N's northern trade routes and the city needed route-security beyond the standard cityguard. Road wardens are technically militia auxiliaries, trained by the Guard Command but funded by the Guild Concordat â reflecting the uneasy marriage between public safety and commercial interest that defines most of @@WMidgaard@@N's institutional arrangements.

~
